            "content": "<p><span class=\"h-card\" translate=\"no\"><a href=\"https://climatejustice.social/@breadandcircuses\" class=\"u-url mention\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">@<span>breadandcircuses</span></a></span> Yup. The life of a child going to school is navigating perils &amp; trauma, with dreadful mental health care. I\u2019m in SoCal. No covid mitigations. Sweltering heat with no relief. My daughter had a live shooter experience in 1st grade. No deaths, but had to hide by herself under her desk for 3 hours, while the other kids were with the teacher behind a bookcase! In High school- bomb threats, gunshots at football games, numerous shooter threats, plus the drills. \ud83d\ude21</p>",
